<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 20:07:49 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>以色列军队做好了迎接赎罪日袭击的准备。一个月后，哈马斯发现了毫无防备的加沙边界</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-braced-for-a-yom-kippur-attack-a-month-later-hamas-found-a-defenseless-gaza-border/0000018e-6225-d507-a1cf-62f7f0a10000</link><description>哈马斯在加沙边境的异常活动导致赎罪日期间驻军人数增加。 ■ 当边境暴力事件平息后，以色列国防军认为这已经吓退了辛瓦尔。 ■ 一位安全消息人士称，“他决定等待”。 “他让军队陷入沉睡”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 20:02:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/idf-braced-for-a-yom-kippur-attack-a-month-later-hamas-found-a-defenseless-gaza-border/0000018e-6225-d507-a1cf-62f7f0a10000</guid></item><item><title>10 月 7 日的“个人、社区和国家创伤”中，以色列将会是什么样子？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/what-israel-will-emerge-from-the-personal-communal-and-national-trauma-of-oct-7/0000018e-60f2-d4b2-afcf-eef6ebfa0000</link><description>和平活动家毛兹伊农在哈马斯袭击中失去了父母。 MK Ahmad Tibi 在加沙失去了 13 名家人。抗议领袖莫兰·泽尔·卡岑斯坦(Moran Zer Katzenstein)从反政府抗议转向哈马斯实施的性暴力。他们所有人都对 10 月 7 日的毁灭性影响有很多话要说</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 19:35:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/what-israel-will-emerge-from-the-personal-communal-and-national-trauma-of-oct-7/0000018e-60f2-d4b2-afcf-eef6ebfa0000</guid></item><item><title>斯莫特里奇撤销了砍伐西岸定居者种植的树木的命令</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-backtracks-order-to-cut-down-settler-planted-trees-in-west-bank/0000018e-61ba-da37-a3ff-77ba8db20000</link><description>在极右翼议会成员攻击以色列军队决定将定居者在巴勒斯坦私人土地上种植的树木连根拔起后，斯莫特里奇部长推翻了他领导的民政管理局的决定</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 19:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/smotrich-backtracks-order-to-cut-down-settler-planted-trees-in-west-bank/0000018e-61ba-da37-a3ff-77ba8db20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军公布 10 月 7 日被杀的军队观察员的录音</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/idf-releases-recording-of-army-spotter-killed-on-october-7/0000018e-623f-d541-a78e-ffffd4bb0000</link><description>19 岁的罗尼·埃谢尔 (Roni Eshel) 在纳哈尔奥兹基地服役，于 10 月 7 日与其他 14 名观察员一起被杀，其中 6 人被哈马斯扣为人质。她的父亲描述了这段录音，其中她报告了哈马斯袭击的开始，“再次提醒人们军队失败的严重性”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 19:08:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/idf-releases-recording-of-army-spotter-killed-on-october-7/0000018e-623f-d541-a78e-ffffd4bb0000</guid></item><item><title>伊朗已成为事实上的核国家吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/has-iran-become-a-de-facto-nuclear-state/0000018e-61d8-d507-a1cf-63de494b0000</link><description>10 月 7 日的事件以及随后的加沙战争是否给德黑兰提供了跨越所有相关门槛的黄金机会？关注伊朗前官员阿里·阿克巴尔·萨利希的表态</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 18:38:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/has-iran-become-a-de-facto-nuclear-state/0000018e-61d8-d507-a1cf-63de494b0000</guid></item><item><title>你需要知道的第 167 天：美国起草联合国停火决议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-167-u-s-drafts-un-resolution-for-cease-fire/0000018e-61f9-d66c-a7fe-65fb91cd0000</link><description>以色列安全官员不顾哈马斯和总理内塔尼亚胡的反对，推动计划招募与哈马斯无关的巴勒斯坦领导人来分发加沙援助。 以色列国防军：600名恐怖分子在希法医院被捕。 美国起草了一项联合国决议，呼吁“立即停止火灾与释放人质有关 ■ 众议院议长迈克·约翰逊表示，他计划邀请内塔尼亚胡向国会发表讲话 ■ 战争结束 167 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 18:01:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/what-you-need-to-know-day-167-u-s-drafts-un-resolution-for-cease-fire/0000018e-61f9-d66c-a7fe-65fb91cd0000</guid></item><item><title>游客可能不喜欢特拉维夫的新城市博物馆，但它不适合他们</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tourists-may-not-like-tel-avivs-new-city-museum-but-its-not-for-them/0000018e-5781-d2a6-adef-d7d7763a0000</link><description>在特拉维夫旧市政厅改建的博物馆中，当地人有机会对第一个现代希伯来城市的传说产生怀疑，而邻近的雅法在每一个展览中都有发言权。即使是大灾难也没有被掩盖</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:55:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-magazine/.premium/tourists-may-not-like-tel-avivs-new-city-museum-but-its-not-for-them/0000018e-5781-d2a6-adef-d7d7763a0000</guid></item><item><title>新调查显示，犹太裔美国人和穆斯林美国人在以色列-加沙战争问题上存在明显分歧</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/sharp-fault-lines-among-jewish-and-muslim-americans-over-gaza-war-new-survey-reveals/0000018e-61ff-d507-a1cf-63ff27b50000</link><description>调查显示，大多数美国人认为以色列打击哈马斯的理由是合理的，但相信以色列在加沙战争中的行为将使以色列人更加安全的人要少得多</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:26:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/sharp-fault-lines-among-jewish-and-muslim-americans-over-gaza-war-new-survey-reveals/0000018e-61ff-d507-a1cf-63ff27b50000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的哈斯巴拉正在失败。那是好消息</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-hasbara-is-failing-thats-good-news/0000018e-61b1-d66c-a7fe-65b3c7f50000</link><description>多年来，内塔尼亚胡让以色列人相信，原话比战略更重要，油嘴滑舌的借口比自我反省或实质内容更重要。加沙战争暴露了对哈斯巴拉的信仰已成为一种负担</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 17:20:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-hasbara-is-failing-thats-good-news/0000018e-61b1-d66c-a7fe-65b3c7f50000</guid></item><item><title>来自耶路撒冷的 MAGA 参议员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/the-maga-senator-from-jerusalem/0000018e-618c-dde2-a5df-7bed7e9b0000</link><description>本杰明·内塔尼亚胡不擅长民主、国家安全和外交关系，但他擅长一件事：摧毁美国在以色列问题上宝贵的两党合作</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 16:37:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/the-maga-senator-from-jerusalem/0000018e-618c-dde2-a5df-7bed7e9b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可以而且必须在不让加沙平民挨饿的情况下与哈马斯作战</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-can-and-must-fight-hamas-without-starving-gazan-civilians-to-death/0000018e-6014-d411-a3df-f0dedd910000</link><description>以色列向加沙提供粮食援助的缓慢行为是不合情理的：这无异于折磨平民，甚至让长期的朋友也变成了震惊的批评者。但以色列可以在不帮助哈马斯的情况下减轻这种不必要的痛苦</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:40:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-can-and-must-fight-hamas-without-starving-gazan-civilians-to-death/0000018e-6014-d411-a3df-f0dedd910000</guid></item><item><title>耶路撒冷将举行普林节游行，尽管加沙人质亲属请求取消</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-to-hold-purim-parade-despite-gaza-hostages-relatives-plea-to-cancel-it/0000018e-6115-d092-afcf-79d72d040000</link><description>加沙人质的家人称耶路撒冷选择扣留阿德洛亚达“缺乏敏感性和团结”，并指责其是出于经济动机。该市否认，称他们的目的是给该市的孩子们带来快乐的经历，“这场战争的一些英雄”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 14:29:02 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/jerusalem-to-hold-purim-parade-despite-gaza-hostages-relatives-plea-to-cancel-it/0000018e-6115-d092-afcf-79d72d040000</guid></item><item><title>以色列预备役士兵杀死了不构成威胁的62岁巴勒斯坦男子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reserve-soldier-kills-62-year-old-palestinian-man-who-posed-no-threat/0000018e-60f6-d702-a58e-68f7bd900000</link><description>宪兵将调查在以色列国防军地区防御营服役的预备役士兵，该营由招募来保护西岸定居点的定居者组成</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:58:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israeli-reserve-soldier-kills-62-year-old-palestinian-man-who-posed-no-threat/0000018e-60f6-d702-a58e-68f7bd900000</guid></item><item><title>以色列高等法院命令国家允许将两名母亲列入孩子的出生证明上</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/high-court-orders-state-to-allow-two-mothers-to-be-listed-on-childs-birth-certificate/0000018e-60c4-d03d-a7ff-e1e78c860000</link><description>针对八年前九对女同性恋夫妇提交的请愿书，高等法院裁定，对同性伴侣子女的出生证明进行任何区别“可能会发出一种冒犯性的信息，即这些关系在本质和质量上是不同的”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:31:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/high-court-orders-state-to-allow-two-mothers-to-be-listed-on-childs-birth-certificate/0000018e-60c4-d03d-a7ff-e1e78c860000</guid></item><item><title>“一片混乱”：在加沙，以色列国防军使用了 70 年前用于训练的弹药和炮弹</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</link><description>试图将弹药、非正规货物和“印度炸药”保存在分解的麻袋中，造成了后勤和行动上的噩梦，使炮兵部队难以协助作战部队，并增加了出错和错过目标的风险</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:20:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/a-huge-mess-in-gaza-idf-used-70-year-old-munitions-and-shells-intended-for-training/0000018e-5db4-d4b2-afcf-dfb626a90000</guid></item><item><title>如果加沙儿童挨饿，以色列将永远失去道德合法性</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-gazas-children-starve-israel-will-lose-its-moral-legitimacy-forever/0000018e-5c96-d3c4-a7cf-7dd6e7720000</link><description>“儿童已开始死于明显的饥饿”：如果以色列继续在加沙发动战争，同时阻碍大规模粮食援助的提供，它将被视为现代记忆中最严重的人道主义危机之一的主要根源</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 12:06:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-opinion/.premium/if-gazas-children-starve-israel-will-lose-its-moral-legitimacy-forever/0000018e-5c96-d3c4-a7cf-7dd6e7720000</guid></item><item><title>拜登计划停止拉法行动并提醒内塔尼亚胡：以色列需要美国</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/biden-plans-to-halt-the-rafah-op-and-remind-netanyahu-israel-needs-america-more-than-ever/0000018e-5e8d-d4b2-afcf-de9fa5760000</link><description>尽管与美国关系紧张，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡仍继续谈论“全面胜利”，但他派遣代表团前往华盛顿的事实凸显了两国之间的力量平衡</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 04:00:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/biden-plans-to-halt-the-rafah-op-and-remind-netanyahu-israel-needs-america-more-than-ever/0000018e-5e8d-d4b2-afcf-de9fa5760000</guid></item><item><title>摩萨德负责人率领的以色列代表团周五前往卡塔尔进行人质和停火谈判</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-live/idf-chief-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-operation-seeks-to-pressure-hamas-on-hostages/0000018e-5ebb-d27e-a7af-7effa02c0000</link><description>以色列国防军和辛贝特称，超过 600 名恐怖分子在 Al-Shifa 医院被捕，其中包括哈马斯和伊斯兰圣战组织高级官员 ■ 布林肯表示，美国“不能支持”拉法的地面行动 ■ 内塔尼亚胡告诉参议院共和党人，即使以色列也必须这样做在没有美国支持的情况下进入拉法，“我们不会停止” ■ 以色列国防军表示，在以色列领土外拦截了从红海地区发射的可疑空中目标。</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 02:04:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article-live/idf-chief-at-gazas-al-shifa-hospital-operation-seeks-to-pressure-hamas-on-hostages/0000018e-5ebb-d27e-a7af-7effa02c0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列21岁以下国家足球队自1976年以来首次参加奥运会就发现了对手</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-soccer-team-discovers-opponents-in-first-olympic-appearance-since-1976/0000018e-5d68-d411-a3df-ddfacfca0000</link><description>21岁以下国家队将对阵巴拉圭、马里和一支尚未确定的亚洲球队。教练盖伊·吕宋 (Guy Luzon)：“能够成为 48 年来第一支代表以色列参加重大赛事的球队，真是令人兴奋”</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:34:48 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-soccer-team-discovers-opponents-in-first-olympic-appearance-since-1976/0000018e-5d68-d411-a3df-ddfacfca0000</guid></item><item><title>拜登的红线：拉法为何成为美以政治战场</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/bidens-red-line-why-rafah-has-become-a-political-battleground-between-the-u-s-israel/0000018e-5dd5-d092-afcf-7dd7a46d0000</link><description>无论是否发生，仅仅以色列国防军袭击拉法的幽灵就为内塔尼亚胡提供了至关重要的政治资本。拜登政府正中他下怀</description><pubDate>Thu, 21 Mar 2024 00:13:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-03-21/ty-article/.premium/bidens-red-line-why-rafah-has-become-a-political-battleground-between-the-u-s-israel/0000018e-5dd5-d092-afcf-7dd7a46d0000</guid></item></channel></rss>